                   Sandbags available to Belmont Residents


   There are two locations residents can pick up sandbags.

   1) Corporation Yard, 110 Sem Lane to the right of the building in a
   wooden shed.

   2) Belmont City Hall, 1070 Sixth Avenue, northwest corner of the
   parking lot across from the Police cars.


